metadata.description:
Love is everywhere #1

It's 3AM when I am writing this. A time when the Mind stops screaming and the Soul starts expressing what's within.

The world is a messed-up place, not today, it always has been. Because it contains Life. Life has never been perfect, so you and I can call it messed up at any point.

But here comes the magical 4 letter world ~ Love!
This one is the decorator of Life. Finding meaning in life becomes like a vision in an endless tunnel without love.

This collection is dedicated to my belief, Love is everywhere! Yes, it is, seriously!

Remember the taste of food made by your Mom, Grandma, or any other loved one? 
Isn't it tastes magical? 

This magic, We call it Love my dear friend.

I hope that through these pieces, you will be able to find instances of love around you everywhere. 

Love ~ Rory.
